 2002-21662002-12-12,  ,  FIN,  , 
ActCustoms Tariff
PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 2002-8 which eliminates the tariffs on certain motors used to manufacture air filtration and air ventilation units, certain non-woven fabrics used as embroidery backings, diphenylguanidine used to produce rubber mixes, certain plywood backing for flooring and certain acrylic fabric for awnings, as well as extends the temporary tariff relief on certain hemp fabrics used to manufacture clothing.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2003-0004 Publication Date: 2003-01-01
AttachmentsAttachment
